Object.value: Alunno di Benozzo (500299803) 'formerly identified with' Amadeo da Pistoia (500027952);
Although there had been speculation that the anonymous artist named by Berenson as "Alunno di Benozzo" was Amadeo da Pistoia, this is now generally held to be untrue.
A. Staderini, Villa I Tatti, email of 18 July 2010
